NAME
    SHARYANTO::Dist::Util - Dist-related utilities

VERSION
    version 0.01

SYNOPSIS
     use SHARYANTO::Dist::Util qw(
         packlist_for
     );

DESCRIPTION
FUNCTIONS
  packlist_for($mod) => STR
    Find ".packlist" file for module $mod (which can be in the form of
    "Package::SubPkg" or "Package/SubPkg.pm"). Return undef if none is
    found.

SEE ALSO
    SHARYANTO

